@startuml FUXA Startup Sequence
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title FUXA - 서버 시작 순서 (Startup Sequence)

participant "main.js" as MAIN
participant "settings\n(settings.default.js)" as SETT
participant "logger\n(runtime/logger.js)" as LOG
participant "Express\nHTTP Server" as HTTP
participant "API Layer\n(api/index.js)" as API
participant "Runtime Engine\n(runtime/index.js)" as RT
participant "ProjectManager" as PM
participant "PluginsManager" as PLG
participant "UsersManager" as UM
participant "DAQStorage" as DAQ
participant "SchedulerService" as SS
participant "DevicesManager" as DM
participant "AlarmsManager" as AM
participant "ScriptsManager" as SM
participant "NotificatorManager" as NM
participant "JobsManager" as JM

MAIN -> SETT : 설정 파일 로드\n(settings.default.js + 사용자 설정)
MAIN -> LOG : logger 초기화
MAIN -> HTTP : Express + Socket.IO 서버 생성

MAIN -> API : api.init(server, runtime)
API -> HTTP : Express 미들웨어 등록\n(bodyParser, morgan, rateLimit)
API -> HTTP : REST 라우트 등록\n(/api/project, /api/auth, ...)

MAIN -> RT : runtime.init(io, api, settings, logger)

RT -> DAQ : daqstorage.init()
RT -> SS : schedulerStorage.init() → schedulerService.init()

RT -> PLG : plugins.init()
PLG --> RT : 'init-plugins-ok' 이벤트

RT -> UM : users.init()
UM --> RT : 'init-users-ok' 이벤트

RT -> PM : project.init()
PM --> RT : 'init-project-ok' 이벤트

RT -> MAIN : 'init-runtime-ok' 이벤트\n(3개 이벤트 모두 수신 후)

MAIN -> RT : runtime.start()

RT -> PM : project.load()\n(DB에서 뷰/디바이스/알람 읽기)

RT -> DM : devices.init(runtime)
RT -> DM : devices.start()\n(활성 디바이스 순회 → device.start())
DM -> DM : 각 디바이스 드라이버 connect()

RT -> AM : new AlarmsManager(runtime)\nalarmsMgr.load() → start()

RT -> SM : new ScriptsManager(runtime)\nscriptsMgr.start()

RT -> NM : new NotificatorManager(runtime)\nnotificatorMgr.start()

RT -> JM : new JobsManager(runtime)\njobsMgr.start()

MAIN -> HTTP : server.listen(PORT)
MAIN -> LOG : "FUXA v{version} started on port {PORT}"

note over DM, AM
  디바이스 폴링과 알람 체크는
  각각 독립적인 setInterval()로 실행됩니다.
end note

@enduml
